RootCauseAnalysis - INFO - [State Update] {"consensus_iteration": 3, "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_task_instruction": "当前处于【假设验证阶段】。\n待验证的根因假设是：'checkoutservice-1 root cause of high server_error_ratio and error_ratio, affecting frontend-2's performance.'。\n请基于 Trace 数据判断该假设是否成立。\n重点：请在返回 JSON 的 'stance' 字段中明确标记 'SUPPORT' 或 'OPPOSE'。", "trace_analysis_findings": "通过分析调用链数据，我们可以得出以下有关假设 \"checkoutservice-1 是根因，导致 server_error_ratio 和 error_ratio 高，进而影响 frontend-2 的性能\" 的结论：\n\n### 分析结果\n\n1. **延迟指标:**\n   - `checkoutservice-1` 在调用 `hipstershop.EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation` 时，异常期间的平均耗时达到了 2703051 ms，而正常期间的平均耗时为 24511 ms，延迟倍数为 110.3 倍，显著高于2。\n   - `frontend-2` 直接调用 `checkoutservice-1` 时，异常平均耗时为 2979958 ms，而正常平均耗时为154721 ms，延迟倍数达到了 19.26 倍。\n\n2. **错误状态:**\n   - `checkoutservice-1` 在调用 `hipstershop.EmailService/SendOrderConfirmation` 时，出现了频繁的连接错误，状态信息为 \"connection error\" 和 \"server misbehaving\"。\n\n3. **调用关系及错误传播路径:**\n   - 延迟和错误主要集中在 `checkoutservice-1`，尤其是在调用下游的 Email Service 时，显示出明显的瓶颈。\n   - `frontend-2` 的性能受到 `checkoutservice-1` 的影响，由于其作为上游，前者调用后者的耗时显著增加。\n\n### 结论\n\n基于以上数据分析，可以支持以下假设：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->emailservice\", \"frontend->checkoutservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常期间调用 email service 时，耗时显著上升，延迟倍数为 110.3 倍，状态为连接错误。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"checkoutservice->emailservice\",\n      \"evidence\": \"调用 checkoutservice 的平均耗时显著增加，影响 frontend-2 的性能。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n`checkoutservice-1` 是造成服务链异常的根因，尤其是在对 `Email Service` 的调用过程中暴露出的延迟和错误率问题。建议进一步调查 Email Service 的连接问题和诊断 `checkoutservice-1` 的健康状况以解决故障。", "log_analysis_findings": "根据日志数据，我们发现以下信息来验证假设：\n\n### 提取信息\n- **日志概况**:\n  - 服务名: `checkoutservice`\n  - Pod 名: `checkoutservice-1`\n  - 节点名: `aiops-k8s-08`\n  - 错误消息: 发送订单确认邮件时失败，出现 RPC 错误，描述了连接错误（服务器行为异常）\n  - 出现频次: 88 次\n\n### 识别错误模式\n- **错误详述**: “failed to send order confirmation to \"someone@example.com\": rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice on 10.233.33.139:53: server misbehaving\"”\n  - `transport: Error while dialing` - 网络传输问题\n  - `lookup emailservice` - DNS 查询失败\n  - `server misbehaving` - 服务器异常行为\n\n### 特殊故障模式识别\n- **DNS 故障模式**:\n  - 日志中包含 `transport: Error while dialing` 和 `lookup emailservice`，指出 DNS 服务故障问题，同时 `server misbehaving` 是明确的服务器异常标志。\n\n### JSON 输出分析结果\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"dns\", \"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"server misbehaving\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"DNS failure and server misbehaving causing rpc error\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to send order confirmation...: transport: Error while dialing dial tcp: lookup emailservice\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**结论**: 根据日志数据，当前假设得到支持：(checkoutservice-1 是根因，高 server_error_ratio 和 error_ratio 影响 frontend-2 的性能)。故障是由于 DNS 查询失败和服务器异常行为导致的。", "raw_metric_result": {"status": "success", "message": "成功加载metric数据。UUID: 5028909d-391", "anomaly_metrics": "metric_type,service_name,pod_name,node_name,metric_name,normal_median,fault_median,normal_p99,fault_p99,median_change_ratio,p99_change_ratio\nservice,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-1,N/A,server_error_ratio,0.0,30.54,0.0,34.68,2.0,2.0\nservice,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-1,N/A,error_ratio,0.0,30.54,0.0,34.68,2.0,2.0\nservice,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-1,N/A,rrt_max,204545.0,3214684.0,300111.52,19988773.56,1.7607,1.9408\nservice,frontend,frontend-2,N/A,rrt_max,253590.0,3282482.5,372891.04,17953977.12,1.7131,1.9186\nservice,frontend,frontend-0,N/A,rrt_max,229825.0,1464803.5,381865.32,17325417.46,1.4575,1.9137\nservice,checkoutservice,checkoutservice-1,N/A,rrt,7556.95,117262.11,9385.42,328671.15,1.7578,1.8889\nservice,frontend,frontend-